<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bqrbk yạ ḥbyby yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bqrbk yạ ḥbyby yswʿ .. qlby ạsẖthy̱ ybqy̱ ṭwl ạlḥyạẗ
 ạ̹dẖ fy ḥmạk ḥyạty tṭyb .. yạ mn bmwtk fwq ạlṣlyb
 nlt kẖlạṣaⁿạ wʿmraⁿạ jdyd .. nlt slạmaⁿạ mqạmaⁿạ mjyd
 fy ạlsmạ fy dạr ạlnʿym .. ḥtmaⁿạ sạ̉ḥyạ fy dạr ạlhnạ
 fhy ạ̹mtdạd ḥyạty hnạ
 2- brạ̉yk ạ̉htdy fy ạlṭryq .. wydk fy ydy kạlṣdyq
 tẖm ạ̹ly̱ mjd dạr ʿlạk .. tạ̉kẖdẖny ky mạ ạ̉bqy̱ hnạk
 bạlqrb mn ʿrsẖ rby yswʿ .. ạ̉ḥly̱ mkạn fy tlk ạlrbwʿ
 fy ạlsmạ fy dạr ạlnʿym .. fạ̉bqy̱ qrbk ṭwl ạlḥyạẗ
 wạ̉bqy̱ qrbk bʿd ạlḥyạẗ
 3- wjwdy qrbk fḍluⁿ ʿẓym .. whw ạ̹mtyạzuⁿ lkẖạṭyiⁿ̉ ạ̉tẖym
 rdạʾ brk yksw ạlkẖṭạẗ .. wdfʾ ḥbk yʿṭy ạlḥyạẗ
 wrwḥ qdsk rwḥ ạlḥyạẗ .. ynʿsẖ rwḥy wysmw bhạ
 llsmạ fy dạr ạlnʿym .. bqrbk yạ ḥbyby yswʿ
 qlby ạsẖthy̱ ybqy̱ ṭwl ạlḥyạẗ</lyrics>
